               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     <p>I) Col. <locus target="#1a"/>: ጸሎት፡በእንተ፡ሕማመ፡ዓይነ፡ጥላ፡ወዓይነ፡ወርቅ፡ዓይነት፡ባርያ፡ወዓይነ፡አጋንንት፡ቁረኛ፡ወተያያዢ፡ጅን፡…, Prayer against demons and diseases, with “Arabic words” (qalä ˀaräbi)  </p>
                     <p>II) Col. <locus target="#1b"/>: ጸሎት፡በእንተ፡ሕማመ፡ዓይነ፡ጥላ፡ወዓይነ፡ወርቅ፡ደም፡ወደመ፡ከትር፡ውርዝልያ፡ወሾተላይ፡…, ˀAsmat prayer against demons, hemmorhage and diseases</p>
                     <p>III) Col. <locus target="#1b"/>: ጸሎት፡በእንተ፡ደም፡ወደመ፡ከትር፡…, Prayer against hemmorhage</p>
                     <p>IV) Col. <locus target="#1b"/>: ጸሎት፡በእንተ፡ባርያ፡ወሌጌዎን፡ርኩስ፡…, ˀAsmat prayer against</p>
                     <p>V) Two “magic squares” encompassing each <locus target="#25"/>letters; the letters in the two bottom lines (inserted in the cells dificiently) make out the words of Lk <locus target="#1"/>:<locus target="#37"/>እስም፡ አልቦ፡ ነገር፡ ዘይሰአኖ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡</p>
                     <p>VI) Col. <locus target="#2a"/>: ጸሎት፡በእንተ፡ሕማ፡ባርያ፡ወሌጌዎን፡ርኩስ፡ዓይነ፡ጥላ፡ወዓይነ፡ወርቅ፡ዓይነ፡አጋንንት፡ወሰይጣናት፡…, ˀAsmat prayer against demons and diseases</p>
                     <p>VII) Col. <locus target="#2a"/>: ጸሎት፡በእንተ፡ጅን፡…, ˀAsmat prayer against demons</p>
                     <p>VIII) Col. <locus target="#2b"/>: ጸሎት፡በእንተ፡ደም፡ወደመ፡ከትር፡ውርዝልያ፡ወሾተላይ፡…, ˀAsmat prayer against demons, hemmorhage and diseases</p>
                     <p>IX) Col. <locus target="#3a"/>: ጸሎት፡በእንተ፡ሕማመ፡ባርያ፡ወሌጌዎን፡ርኩስ፡ዓይነ፡አጋንንት፡ወሰይጣናት፡…, ˀAsmat prayer against demons and diseases</p>
                     <p>X) Col. <locus target="#3a"/>: ጸሎት፡በእንተ፡ማዕሰረ፡አጋንንት፡ዓይነ፡ሾተላይ፡ወዓይነ፡ጋራት፡…, ˀAsmat prayer against demons and diseases</p>
                     <p>XI) Col. <locus target="#3b"/>: ጸሎት፡በእንተ፡ሕማመ፡ውርዝልያ፡ደም፡ወደመ፡ከትር፡…, ˀAsmat prayer against hemmorhage and for conception</p>
                     <p>XII) Col. <locus target="#3b"/>: በሰይፈ፡ እሳት፡ በሐፀ፡ እሳት፡ መለኮት፡ በፃዕ፡ ፃዕ፡…, ˀAsmat prayer against hemmorhage</p>
                     <p>XIII) Col. <locus target="#3b"/>: ጸሎት፡በእንተ፡ወሊድ፡&lt;…&gt;, ˀAsmat prayer for successfull giving birth</p>
                     
                     
                     
                  </summary>
              
               </msContents>
               <physDesc>
                  <objectDesc form="Scroll">
                     <supportDesc>
                        <extent>
                           <dimensions type="outer">
